{"tid":636893,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鹿晗：當初如果選擇足球 現在可能在英超踢球","createTime":"2018-04-21T10:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T11:20:21.000Z","uid":20634,"like":10,"dislike":500,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"56569b40c7f05d5b5db3f3c2cb50c8f6ac33dec3","tid":636893,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/04/21/8/8a60d370ac0c65c99f2ed14f01a1da21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F8%2F8a60d370ac0c65c99f2ed14f01a1da21.jpg&h=e01eecda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　新浪體育訊 近日，鹿晗在接受採訪時大聊足球。鹿晗坦言，當年曾經想過通過訓練走職業足球的道路，甚至連教練都找好了。為何最後選擇進去演藝圈而放棄足球，鹿晗耿直解釋道：「因為沒時間去踢，年齡也有點大了，就沒有去。」但時至今日，鹿晗對自己的球技仍然很有信心，他表示「當時如果選擇足球的話，現在可能就在英超踢球了」。"},{"pid":"30ed215dccd6be14342809c47497ba0a4cb7b4b5","tid":636893,"uid":20736,"like":300,"dislike":1,"score":299,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:22:29.000Z","msg":"有時啲執波仔都可以踢下個波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踢返個波比啲球員嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd2c6a6623f439b0dfef779fd11072331400d29","tid":636893,"uid":171107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:24:06.000Z","msg":"充滿自信"},{"pid":"72c8942f99788de94c752b0116de1df0a1780329","tid":636893,"uid":81569,"like":157,"dislike":6,"score":151,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:24:14.000Z","msg":"佢呢家應該開心啦<br />\n收入仲多過踢英超"},{"pid":"dcc218731e047bf9376ae38d807dcd665776602f","tid":636893,"uid":34517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"siuma"},{"pid":"eeba58df5e9eb036bda8ecf8badbacf4da7838f3","tid":636893,"uid":12628,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"呢隻老鼠乜水"},{"pid":"5bc1074c7e0f8dce97a1cf7032e790b2c80804ee","tid":636893,"uid":171754,"like":1,